&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3321&quot; title=&quot;2.x single thread/process throughput degraded from 1.8&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-3321&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-3321&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; clio: add pages into writeback cache in batch&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    in ll_write_end(), instead of adding the page into writeback&lt;br/&gt;
